{
  "title": "Ramp FTP Test",
  "description": "Progressive ramp test to find your Functional Threshold Pace. Starting at 60W (~2:58/500m), intensity increases by 20W every minute until failure. Row until you can no longer hold the target pace, then stop. FTP is approximately 65% of peak watts achieved (rowing convention). Works for all fitness levels.",
